          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"coordination-networks-cib-triage\">Coordination networks (CIB triage)</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Detect account clusters acting in concert across behavioural channels,\nvalidated against null models and corroborated across layers.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Sampling caveat:</strong> Capture is a sample, not a census: absence of a co-action is not evidence of absence. Recall is bounded; precision is not affected.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Coordination alone is not malicious - the scorecard ranks clusters for\nhuman review using Phase 1 authenticity + Phase 2 narrative signals.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
